### Health
GET http://localhost:8080/healthz

### Create agent task
POST http://localhost:8080/api/agent/task
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "owner": "rishi.sharma",
  "task": "Check deployment readiness for QA",
  "context": "SSDLC scanner validation demo"
}

### Search memory
GET http://localhost:8080/api/memory/search?owner=rishi.sharma

### DNS diagnostic
GET http://localhost:8080/api/agent/tools/dns?host=example.com

### URL fetch
GET http://localhost:8080/api/agent/fetch?url=https://example.com

### Feedback
POST http://localhost:8080/api/feedback
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "QA Reviewer",
  "message": "Scanner validation feedback"
}
